title: New Securities Offered for Cash, Estimated Gross Proceeds, Public Utility Industry, Total Securities for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1934-1948 (2)--Original Data, 1948-1964. Coverage Includes Electric, Gas, Water, Telephone, Street Railway And Bus Company Issues. The Missing Figure For January 1935 Is Less Than $500,000. Source: Data For 1934-1940: Unpublished Table Furnished By The Survey Of Current Business (Obe-53, August 19, 1958); Data For 1941-1948: Scb Statistical Supplement, 1947 And Subsequent Issues

This NBER data series m10126a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
